data.description: Experience this lovely single-family home nestled on a spacious lot in a quiet  neighborhood. Boasting an inviting open-concept kitchen and living area that seamlessly leads to a backyard overlooking a peaceful green space, this residence offers ample space for family gatherings. Enjoy the convenience of generous storage options, including a large pantry, hall closet, and walk-in closets in each of the four bedrooms. Recent upgrades include a home security system with a doorbell camera, backyard camera, window chimes, a smart thermostat, keyless entry on the front door, and charming farmhouse sink. Located in a family-centric community within walking distance of Yukon's newest Intermediate school, this home is sure to go fast.
